Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(回顧)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:02.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,JOJO的奇妙冒險 前文回顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來 和我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滾 我可沒叫你來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能幫到我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我三年前認識的埃及朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤炎荒繩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}Red Bind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我告訴你它的真面目吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那東西既是惡靈 又非惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承太郎 被你當作惡靈的——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以你的生命能量製造出來的 擁有力量的幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(1023,660)}Vision
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於它會在身邊顯現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此這幻象被命名為——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}Stand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是距今四年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.63,0:01:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從大西洋近非洲海岸打撈上來的一百年前的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棺材？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據我回收調查的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個棺材是你曾曾祖父 即是我的爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喬納森·喬斯達死亡時坐的客船上所載的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被發現時裡面空無一物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我知道裡面是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿布德爾正在追蹤那傢伙的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是邪惡的化身 他的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.68,0:01:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪奧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是從百年的沉睡中甦醒的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而與他戰鬥 正是我們必須肩負的使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在他的後頸上…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這混賬傢伙頭部以下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是我爺爺喬納森·喬斯達被侵佔的肉體啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(avant)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承太郎 等下 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你落東西了哦 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 這是路上小心的吻喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這娘們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再粘著自己的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯—— 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？JoJo？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀 是JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊 JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 四天沒來學校了 都去哪裡了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我說你 幹嘛抱著JoJo的手往上面蹭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別套近乎 快走開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你個醜八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真煩 搓衣板
