Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,710)}醜八怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,710)}醜八怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醜八怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,710)}搓衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴 煩透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他對我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對我說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樹枝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo跌下樓梯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 他反應過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樹枝撐住了沒受什麼傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是樹枝劃到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是掉下來之前劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才會踩空了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能召出很強力的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪那位大人要派我來收拾他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的替身的對手
